    "AMD is a progressive degenerative disorder of the central retina and a leading cause of irreversible vision loss in older adults (14).",
    "Early detection of AMD is crucial for timely intervention and prevention of vision loss.",
    "Still, traditional screening methods rely on trained specialists' manual interpretation of OCT images and fundus photographs (15).",
    "AI, particularly CNNs, has shown promise in automating the analysis of these images for AMD detection and classification (16).",
    "Several studies have developed and validated CNN models for AMD detection using OCT images."
  ],
